<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2024</copyright><pubDate> Mon, 22 Jan 2024 11:55:56 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Meta is letting users uncouple Messenger and Marketplace accounts in the EU]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>几个月来，Meta 一直在与<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/europe-digital-markets-act-005742387.html">欧盟数字市场法案</a>(DMA) 即将出台的法规作斗争，但仅此而已。该公司宣布<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://about.fb.com/news/2024/01/offering-people-more-choice-on-how-they-can-use-our-services-in-the-eu/">将遵守 DMA 的规定</a>，即不得偏袒自己的服务或强迫用户留在其生态系统内。这一决定将极大地影响 Meta 在欧盟的用户体验，包括允许人们在没有 Facebook 帐户的情况下使用<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/facebook-messenger-update-sets-default-end-to-end-encryption-for-chats-and-calls-032841879.html">Messenger</a>和 Facebook Marketplace。 Meta 此前提出上诉，认为这两个平台不应纳入 DMA 管辖范围。</p><p>让步意味着欧盟的 Messenger 和<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/eu-meta-dominance-limiting-competitors-facebook-marketplace-142748760.html">Facebook Marketplace</a>用户现在可以通过独立帐户使用这些服务及其所有功能。 Marketplace 的唯一区别是对话将通过电子邮件进行。除了 Facebook Marketplace 和 Messenger 之外，欧盟委员会对 Meta 的监管还包括 Facebook、Instagram、 <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/whatsapp-adds-disappearing-voice-messages-to-its-roster-of-privacy-features-172813331.html">WhatsApp</a>和 Meta 广告。例如，用户现在可以将 Facebook 和 Instagram 帐户分开，而不是在两个平台之间链接信息。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>欧盟委员会最初指定六家公司为 DMA 的“ <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/eu-confirms-the-six-tech-giants-subject-to-its-strict-new-competition-laws-161917822.html?guccounter=1">看门人</a>”：Alphabet、亚马逊、苹果、字节跳动、Meta 和微软。由于用户、收入和估值等因素，它们之间有 22 项核心平台服务属于该法律的管辖范围。资格还取决于“它们是否在核心平台服务方面为企业和消费者之间提供了重要的门户”。 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-joins-meta-and-bytedance-in-contesting-the-eus-gatekeeper-designation-165915809.html">字节跳动和苹果</a>等公司在 DMA 规定于 2024 年 3 月强制执行之前对其进行了抵制。然而，谷歌（Alphabet 旗下）最近宣布，用户可以阻止其 YouTube 和 Chrome 等平台共享数据。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/meta-is-letting-users-un Couple-messenger-and-marketplace-accounts-in-the-eu-115556543.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/meta-is-letting-users-uncouple-messenger-and-marketplace-accounts-in-the-eu-115556543.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 615f19c4-4068-486c-8d86-9f68dcad9039 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Sarah Fielding]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 22 Jan 2024 11:55:56 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1705925145</ingested><modified> 2024-01-22T12:05:50+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Sarah Fielding]]></category><media:content height="968" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-11%2Faf12d510-8be6-11ee-bed6-bec61b844603&amp;resize=1400%2C968&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=a25ba67ba43225a9c0adbbc03e3358d3ec6985af" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="968" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-11%2Faf12d510-8be6-11ee-bed6-bec61b844603&amp;resize=1400%2C968&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=76215810ad230fe72b3079b5e35ceb521efa63d6" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Francis Mascarenhas / reuters]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[People walk behind a logo of Meta Platforms company, during a conference in Mumbai, India, September 20, 2023. REUTERS/Francis Mascarenhas]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[META PLATFORMS-MESSAGING/WHATSAPP]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Korg's MicroKorg 2 and KingKorg Neo are overdue updates to its virtual analog synthesizers]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> NAMM 2024 即将到来，但 Korg 并没有等待庆祝活动的正式开始。在过去的几天里，该公司宣布了大约十几种新产品。其中包括对该公司两款虚拟模拟合成器的更新，即已有大约 10 年历史的 KingKorg 和已有 22 年历史的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2016-09-01-korg-announces-microkorg-s-with-more-sounds-and-user-presets.html">MicroKorg</a> 。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.korg.com/us/products/synthesizers/kingkorg_neo/index.php">KingKorg Neo</a>与 Korg 最近的其他数字合成器（如<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/korgs-opsix-mk-ii-synth-is-based-on-the-fm-sound-engine-of-the-original-but-with-64-voices-164445223.html">Opsix</a> 、 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/korg-modwave-wavetable-synthesizer-namm-dw-8000-172025182.html">Modwave</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2020-01-07-korgs-wavestate-classic-90s-vector-synth-wavestation.html">Wavestate）</a>采用相同的 37 键外形。但这里的核心是该公司的XMT（扩展建模技术）虚拟模拟声音引擎。它不是世界上最令人信服的模拟仿真，但它确实有一些特点。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="40fca919d37845a3adfbd0a845951c64"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Dx2N3KA5dow?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div></div><p>它是一个多音色合成器，每个音色都能够分层或分割成不同的声音，并具有三个振荡器可供使用。振荡器前端有 138 种不同的选项可供选择，范围从基本波形到 PCM 样本。还有 18 种不同的滤波器仿真可供选择，包括经典的<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2020-01-14-korg-ms-20-fs-synth-full-sized-reissue.html">MS-20</a> 。还有两个低频振荡器、两个包络以及从典型的延迟和混响到放大器模拟器和声音破坏抽取器的一整套效果。</p><p>也许最令人兴奋的是 16 频段声码器和随附的鹅颈麦克风。但是，KingKorg Neo 并不是这家传奇制造商唯一一款带有声码器的新型合成器。它还用<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.korg.com/us/products/synthesizers/microkorg2/">MicroKorg 2</a>更新了其标志性的 MicroKorg。</p><p>最初的 MicroKorg 于 2002 年推出，并成为有史以来最畅销的合成器之一。事实上，到 2023 年 5 月，Korg 仍在推出原版的迭代版本，并通过 Crystal 特别版庆祝其数十年的成功。 </p><div id="fa62a1b4d02e4272b1091e02c1ecce9a"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JTlWEziuZc4?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div></div><p>新版本具有非常相似的外形，包括小尺寸、鹅颈麦克风、电池供电的能力以及用于导航补丁的大表盘，这些补丁仍然按类型排序。但引擎盖下是一个新的声音引擎，前面有一个 2.8 英寸彩色显示屏，可以简化声音设计。还有一个内置循环录音机，这应该使它成为独奏表演者更强大的乐器。</p><p> KingKorg Neo 预计将于 2 月份开始发货，售价为<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Sweetwater Sound;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=e54dc56f-69db-417f-9610-572a1a179058&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Sweetwater+Sound&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcqI8AtNqBLSfZ3K0Gqm4BKkdrPasqaZqbiO3UMAMNL6&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sweetwater.com%2Fstore%2Fdetail%2FKingKorgNeo--korg-kingkorg-neo-37-key-virtual-analog-synthesizer-and-vocoder" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.sweetwater.com/store/detail/KingKorgNeo--korg-kingkorg-neo-37-key-virtual-analog-synthesizer-and-vocoder">1,000 美元</a>。不过，我们还得再等一段时间才能看到 MicroKorg 2，它应该会在 6 月上市，不过目前还没有定价消息。希望它能像原来那样落在 500 美元的范围内。 MicroKorg 如此成功的部分原因在于，即使是最低级的合成器爱好者也可以完全使用它。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/korgs-microkorg-2-and-kingkorg-neo-are-overdue-updates-to-its-virtual-analog-synthesizers-110005853.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/korgs-microkorg-2-and-kingkorg-neo-are-overdue-updates-to-its-virtual-analog-synthesizers-110005853.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4882f4fc-d5ed-4c41-8c47-2f0590b14ca1 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Terrence O&amp;#39;Brien]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 22 Jan 2024 11:00:05 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1705888849</ingested><modified> 2024-01-22T02:00:54+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Terrence O&#39;Brien]]></category><media:content height="687" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2Fb9062d20-b8c2-11ee-befa-882aaa2187e9&amp;resize=1400%2C687&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=79449be65ba90fc1e664bd81637984a99162f1b2" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="687" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2Fb9062d20-b8c2-11ee-befa-882aaa2187e9&amp;resize=1400%2C687&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=8dcf81fa869163bfe1886a16871ad52a0d2577b9" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Korg]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Korg MicroKorg 2]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Korg MicroKorg 2]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple might have sold up to 180,000 Vision Pro headsets over pre-order weekend]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>苹果售价 3,499 美元的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-vision-pro-hands-on-redux-immersive-video-disney-app-floating-keyboard-and-a-little-screaming-180006222.html">Vision Pro</a>并不适合所有人，事实上，最新的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-vision-pro-pre-orders-are-now-open-130056024.html">预购</a>预估反映了这款<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-tells-developers-not-to-call-their-ar-and-vr-apps-ar-or-vr-apps-085136127.html"><del>VR</del></a>空间计算设备的起步缓慢。根据分析师<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://medium.com/@mingchikuo/vision-pro%E9%A6%96%E9%80%B1%E6%9C%AB%E9%A0%90%E8%B3%BC%E6%AA%A2%E8%A6%96-%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E4%BD%86%E9%9A%B1%E6%86%82%E6%B5%AE%E7%8F%BE-vision-pros-first-weekend-pre-order-review-expectations-in-line-0450c1effe66">Min-Chi Kuo 根据预购库存和运输时间的</a>计算，他估计该公司在上周末售出了 160,000 至 180,000 台 Vision Pro 耳机。这已经远远超过了郭明池<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/mingchikuo/status/1745516663867629912">早前定下的2月2日首发的6万至8万台的产量数字</a>，也难怪Vision Pro在开启预购后立即售空。</p><p>虽然这听起来像是个好消息，但郭指出，由于前 48 小时内的运输时间保持不变，这可能表明在大量用户和铁杆粉丝完成预订后，需求会迅速下降。相比之下，iPhone 订单通常“在预订开启后 24 至 48 小时内，发货时间会稳步增加”。但当然，Vision Pro 目前的状态并不适合普通消费者，特别是考虑到缺乏<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apples-vision-pro-wont-have-access-to-youtube-and-spotify-apps-at-launch-083434306.html">YouTube、Spotify</a>或<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-wont-launch-an-app-for-the-apple-vision-pro-at-least-right-now-120520406.html">Netflix</a>等一些主流应用程序。更不用说令人瞠目结舌的 3,499 美元的基本价格，据<em>彭博社的</em>马克·古尔曼 (Mark Gurman) 早些时候报道，苹果可能会在晚些时候发布一款价格在 1,500 至 2,500 美元之间的<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-may-cut-eyesight-display-and-mac-chip-for-its-cheaper-vision-pro-204548008.html">更便宜的型号</a>。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>郭补充道，即使该设备按照最初生产量 8 万台的上限计算，也仅占苹果 12 亿活跃用户的 0.007% 左右，这使得 Vision Pro 在苹果公司眼中是“非常小众的产品”。库比蒂诺。也就是说，这家科技巨头需要在这款耳机全球发布之前以某种方式吸引并维持对该耳机的需求，有传言称，全球发布将在今年 WWDC 之前的某个时间（可能是 6 月）进行。与此同时，苹果公司还忙着在其美国旗舰店设立演示区，希望通过<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/if-you-want-to-demo-the-vision-pro-at-an-apple-store-prepare-to-be-there-a-while-172207401.html">25 分钟的演示</a>来增加销量。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apple-might-have-sold-up-to-180000-vision-pro-headsets-over-pre-order-weekend-081727344.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-might-have-sold-up-to-180000-vision-pro-headsets-over-pre-order-weekend-081727344.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 577e4992-664d-4bf3-9676-ecfcb610c4ac </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Richard Lai]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 22 Jan 2024 08:17:27 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1705911448</ingested><modified> 2024-01-22T08:17:31+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Richard Lai]]></category><media:content height="759" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2Fa1190800-b8f3-11ee-bee3-51863878b85d&amp;resize=1400%2C759&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=10f40417b56a0e756eb37b88e405bb041f92fcec" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="759" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2Fa1190800-b8f3-11ee-bee3-51863878b85d&amp;resize=1400%2C759&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=10f40417b56a0e756eb37b88e405bb041f92fcec" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Apple might have sold up to 180,000 Vision Pro headsets over pre-order weekend]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Doomed crypto firm Terraform Labs files for bankruptcy in the US]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Terraform Labs 是一家因 TerraUSD 和 Luna 稳定币崩溃而从加密市场<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/south-korean-prosecutors-interpol-terraform-labs-ceo-do-kwon-060719940.html">损失 400 亿美元</a>的公司，最终于周日根据美国破产法第 11 章申请破产保护。 <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/crypto-s-terraform-files-for-bankruptcy-as-do-kwon-awaits-fate"><em>彭博社</em></a>报道称，该加密货币公司的估计资产和负债均在 1 亿至 5 亿美元之间，估计债权人数量在 100 至 199 人之间。联合创始人兼前首席执行官 Do Kwon 被列为该公司的大股东。 92%，其注册地址位于公司注册地新加坡。</p><p>去年 3 月<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/terraform-labs-founder-do-kwon-handed-four-month-sentence-in-montenegro-100507468.html">，Kwon 及其同伙因持伪造护照旅行而在黑山被捕</a>，目前 Kwon 仍在监狱中，直到被引渡到美国（据<em>彭博社</em>报道，可能会在 3 月中旬），他将在美国面临<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sec-charges-terraform-and-ceo-with-fraud-145347680.html">证券欺诈指控</a>。这位企业家也因类似指控在他的祖国韩国被通缉，据报道，这导致他、他的家人和一些主要 Terraform Labs 人员在 2022 年 4 月至 5 月期间逃往新加坡。就在国际刑警组织将他列入<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/interpol-red-notice-terraform-founder-do-kwon-104327535.html">“红色通缉令”</a>之前不久在当年 9 月的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/interpol-red-notice-terraform-founder-do-kwon-104327535.html">名单</a>上，权否认自己“在逃”，但最终发现他的假护照表明事实并非如此。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Kwon 很可能会与其他知名人士一起陷入加密货币的衰落，即 FTX 名声大噪的<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sam-bankman-fried-sent-to-jail-for-witness-tampering-202906192.html">Sam Bankman-Fried</a>和前摄氏度网络首席执行官<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/celsius-founder-alex-mashinsky-arrested-and-charged-with-fraud-170235270.html">Alex Mashinsky</a> 。与此同时，Coinbase 继续<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/coinbase-wants-its-sec-lawsuit-dismissed-arguing-it-doesnt-deal-in-securities-170056685.html">反对</a>SEC 指控其非法运营未注册的国家证券交易所、经纪商和清算机构。<em>彭博社</em>分析师 Elliott Stein<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/NYCStein/status/1748334299957367287">最近表示</a>，Coinbase 可能最早在本季度（如果不是在第二季度末）就被全面解雇。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/doomed-crypto-firm-terraform-labs-files-for-bankruptcy-in-the-us-055731287.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/doomed-crypto-firm-terraform-labs-files-for-bankruptcy-in-the-us-055731287.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> bdde14d0-b829-4d9b-a377-fd673a2a62c9 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Richard Lai]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 22 Jan 2024 05:57:31 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1705906933</ingested><modified> 2024-01-22T07:02:16+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Richard Lai]]></category><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2F129e2310-b8e1-11ee-ba8f-331b1ff1f2c4&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=743aa2132f330f52e829ffeb31ca2f56f647a70c" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2F129e2310-b8e1-11ee-ba8f-331b1ff1f2c4&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=43bb56e86a115fb6969c63ccaf2139e2785129ca" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[REUTERS / Reuters]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Do Kwon, the cryptocurrency entrepreneur, who created the failed Terra (UST) stablecoin, is taken to court in Podgorica, Montenegro, March 24, 2023. REUTERS/Stevo Vasiljevic MONTENEGRO OUT. NO COMMERCIAL OR EDITORIAL SALES IN MONTENEGRO]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Do Kwon is arrested in Podgorica]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[OpenAI suspends developer over ChatGPT bot that impersonated a presidential candidate]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>据<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/2024/01/20/openai-dean-phillips-ban-chatgpt/" data-original-link="https://www.washingtonpost.com/technology/2024/01/20/openai-dean-phillips-ban-chatgpt/"><em><ins>《华盛顿邮报》</ins></em></a>报道，OpenAI 已暂停 Dean.Bot 背后的开发人员，这是一款由 ChatGPT 驱动的机器人，旨在冒充民主党总统候选人迪恩·菲利普斯 (Dean Phillips)，以帮助支持他的竞选活动。该聊天机器人是由人工智能初创公司 Delphi 为支持 Phillips 的超级 PAC We Deserve Better 创建的。</p><p> Dean.Bot 并没有全力假装成 Phillips 本人。在与 Dean.Bot 互动之前，网站访问者会看到一份描述聊天机器人性质的免责声明。尽管如此，这种类型的使用直接违反了 OpenAI 的政策。该公司发言人在给<em>《华盛顿邮报》</em>的一份声明中证实了开发商的停职。就在几周前，OpenAI 发表了一篇冗长的<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://openai.com/blog/how-openai-is-approaching-2024-worldwide-elections" data-original-link="https://openai.com/blog/how-openai-is-approaching-2024-worldwide-elections"><ins>博客文章</ins></a>，介绍其为<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/openai-lays-out-its-misinformation-strategy-ahead-of-2024-elections-022549912.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/openai-lays-out-its-misinformation-strategy-ahead-of-2024-elections-022549912.html"><ins>防止 2024 年选举前滥用其技术而采取的</ins></a>措施，特别引用“聊天机器人冒充候选人”作为不允许的例子。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-01/9b7d0340-b8a5-11ee-abff-4eff7315d64e" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-01/9b7d0340-b8a5-11ee-abff-4eff7315d64e" style="height:936px;width:1823px;" alt="针对国会议员迪恩·菲利普斯 (Dean Phillips) 的聊天机器人的免责声明"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">迪恩·博特</div></figure><p>OpenAI 还在其博客文章中表示，它“不允许人们构建用于政治竞选和游说的应用程序”。根据<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/elections/2024/01/18/ai-tech-biden/" data-original-link="https://www.washingtonpost.com/elections/2024/01/18/ai-tech-biden/"><em><ins>《华盛顿邮报》</ins></em></a>早些时候的报道，Dean.Bot 的目的是与潜在的支持者互动并传播候选人的信息。根据<em>《华盛顿邮报</em>》的调查，Delphi 最初从机器人中删除了 ChatGPT，并使其与其他开源工具一起运行，最终在周五晚上 OpenAI 介入后完全占领了该机器人。</p><p>如果您现在访问该网站，您仍然会看到免责声明，但聊天机器人本身由于“技术困难”而关闭，向访问者显示以下消息：“抱歉，DeanBot 现在正在参加竞选活动！” Engadget 已联系 OpenAI 征求意见。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/openai-suspends-developer-over-chatgpt-bot-that-impersonated-a-presidential-candidate-214854456.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/openai-suspends-developer-over-chatgpt-bot-that-impersonated-a-presidential-candidate-214854456.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 50bf048d-eea7-45b3-812c-a076d392c475 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Cheyenne MacDonald]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Sun, 21 Jan 2024 21:48:54 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1705873736</ingested><modified> 2024-01-21T21:49:01+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Cheyenne MacDonald]]></category><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2F90c602a0-b8a3-11ee-a7b3-92d97b6440b3&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=42c1ccf3557324a3713efa3d9b2a6133d937289a" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CD